{"type": "article", "id": 22098, "title": "别吃了，喝点果蔬汁吧｜Enjoy、Juicifi", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 3910, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">过年在家吃饭，还计算卡路里。这不仅自虐，还得小心亲戚那张嘴。但吃了这么多天大鱼大肉过后，肠胃确实需要休息一下。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001920VbaKi7xQcjfEqGLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">你可以试着在 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/juicifi-300+-raw-organic-juicing/id980756533?mt=8\">Juicifi </a>里找一款果汁配方尝一尝。这款应用里搜集了超过 300 种配方。如果你想养成每天一杯果汁的生活习惯，一年也够喝了。Juicifi 还内置定时喝果汁的闹钟。</p>\n<p class=\"\">问题是，冰箱里可能没有配方里的水果，甚至压根儿什么都没有。美食团购应用 Enjoy（<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/enjoy-jing-xuan-xian-liang/id943837902?mt=8\">iPhone</a>｜<a href=\"http://www.wandoujia.com/apps/com.ricebook.highgarden\">Andorid</a>） 里倒是能找到外送果蔬汁的店。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001920V7inO4EWQRPY6STs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">不过，目前只在北京、上海、成都做生意的 Enjoy，可能需要你今天已经成功挤回了这些城市。</p>\n\n\n"}